  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment completed. All seven assessed factors are documented with detailed rationale; six factors are scoped out at MRL 2. The overall evidence package supports a Medium assurance conclusion consistent with the regulatory submission requirements.",
