      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version control with documented test suite; all simulation runs must be traceable to a specific solver build.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used under an institutional software quality management plan. Version control records, regression test logs, and build identifiers are archived in the project repository. All simulation input decks are stored with checksums, enabling full reproducibility of results. SQA requirements at Gradation 2 are satisfied."
