      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases relevant to rotating machinery flows.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against standard CFD benchmark problems including lid-driven cavity flow, rotating disk flow, and the FDA nozzle benchmark. Internal verification reports confirm that the pressure-velocity coupling and turbulence model implementations produce results within accepted tolerances for the relevant flow regimes. No anomalies were identified in the solver verification record applicable to this COU."
