      "acceptanceCriteria": "The chosen turbulence and hemolysis model forms must be documented and justified relative to the flow physics of the COU.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-ω turbulence model is appropriate for the transitional and mildly separated flows present in the centrifugal pump at the specified operating points. The power-law hemolysis model is the standard approach for this class of device. Model form selection is documented in the simulation plan and justified by reference to published validation studies for similar pump geometries."
    },
