      "rationale": "Pump geometry was derived from the FDA generic pump CAD files (publicly available). Fluid properties were measured experimentally and are documented in the fluid characterization report. Boundary conditions (flow rates, rotational speed) are traceable to the experimental test matrix. All inputs are documented and traceable at the level required for MRL 2."
